<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Payment Failed</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap');

        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f4f8;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .fail-icon {
            font-size: 60px;
            color: #d9534f;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            color: #d9534f;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .details {
            text-align: left;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .details p {
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .details strong {
            color: #333;
        }

        .actions {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .actions a {
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .try_btn {
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            font-size: 16px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            background-color: #ff8f9c;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .contact_btn {
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            font-size: 16px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            background-color: #96999b;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .try_btn:hover {
            background-color: #fc5d70;
        }

        .contact_btn:hover {
            background-color: #545b62;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 20px;
                margin: 20px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }

            p {
                font-size: 16px;
            }

            .actions {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 10px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="fail-icon">✖</div>
        <h1>Payment Failed</h1>
        <p>We’re sorry, your payment could not be processed. Please try again or contact support.</p>
        <div class="details">
            <p><strong>Transaction ID:</strong> TXN789012</p>
            <p><strong>Date:</strong> May 11, 2025</p>
            <p><strong>Error:</strong> Invalid card details</p>
        </div>
        <div class="actions">
            <a href="/" class="try_btn">Try Again</a>
            <a href="/" class="contact_btn">Contact Support</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>